public final class MainFrame
extends javax.swing.JFrame
implements ProlStreamManager, java.lang.Runnable, javax.swing.event.UndoableEditListener, java.awt.event.WindowListener, javax.swing.event.DocumentListener, javax.swing.event.HyperlinkListener, TraceListener

The class implements the main frame of the Prol Pad IDE (a small UI utility to edit and run prol scripts) because it is a very specialized auxiliary class, it is not described very precisely

Author:
Igor Maznitsa (igor.maznitsa@igormaznitsa.com)
